# Campus Lost & Found App 📱

A simple Android application that helps students post and find lost/found items inside a college campus.

## 🚀 Features
- User can post **Lost** or **Found** items
- Add item details: name, location, description
- Upload item image (stored as Base64 in Firestore)
- View all posted items in a list (RecyclerView)
- Firebase Firestore integration

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Android Studio (Java)
- Firebase Firestore Database
- RecyclerView
- Base64 Image Encoding/Decoding

## 📂 Firebase Used
- Firebase Firestore (for storing item details + Base64 images)

## 📱 Screens Included
- Main Activity (List of Lost/Found items)
- Add Item Activity (Upload lost/found post)

## ⚙️ How to Run the Project
1. Clone the repository
2. Open in Android Studio
3. Add your own `google-services.json` file in `app/`
4. Sync Gradle
5. Run on Emulator or Physical Device

